arrayIterator Class

Defined in: src/iterator/array.js:17
Module: base
Parent Module: iterator

Default initialization, custom .at method.

In addition to iterator methods, arrayIterators also have the following Array methods: concat, join, pop, push, reverse, shift, slice, sort, splice, and unshift
